Manual Analysis.description: Indicator of manual analysis (conducted if PDP sleep duration was outside thresholds of >16 hours or <3 hours). Value 0 indicates no manual analysis; Value 1 indicates manual analysis

bed_time_FINAL.description: If Manual Analysis = 0, bed_time_FINAL = bed_time_PDP. If Manual Analysis =1, Bed_time_FINAL is the bed time determined by the manual analysis

wake_time_FINAL.description: If Manual Analysis = 0, wake_time_FINAL = wake_time_PDP. If Manual Analysis =1, wake_time_FINAL is the wake time determined by the manual analysis

SleepDur_FINAL.description: wake_time_FINAL - Bed_time_FINAL. (ie - sleep duration based on the variables bed_time_final and wake_time_final

Est_MI.description: Movement Index (Sleep Quality Measurement). Based on bed_time_FINAL and wake_time_FINAL sleep window

Est_FI.description: Fragmentation Index (Sleep Quality Measurement). Based on bed_time_FINAL and wake_time_FINAL sleep window

bed_time_FINAL_dec.description: Bed Time Final reported as a decimal

wake_time_FINAL_dec.description: Wake Time final reported as a decimal
